	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Montreal</placeName> <date>26th May 5624</date></p>
				<p>Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">If there are no<lb/> &#8220;Occident traces&#8221; in the printed off<lb/> matter&#44; we will not say anything<lb/> more of the few errors the Biography<lb/> contained.  But please look&#44;<lb/> and <hi rend="underline">let me know</hi> whether<lb/> the Occident head lines have<lb/> indeed been retained.  I need not<lb/> ask you to be careful to remove<lb/> the traces in succeeding portions.<lb/>  If 130 have been printed off<lb/> they will be enough.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">As I am writing<lb/> hurriedly&#44; I cannot stop to<lb/> recollect where <add>Hebrew</add> occurs</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>in the copy&#44; nor did I know<lb/> that I omitted a letter in shilling&#39;s<add>&#63;</add>.<lb/>  But nothing is more probable.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I am sorry you took the<lb/> trouble to look up the queried<lb/> word in the last copy in a Spanish<lb/> dictionary.  The word being<lb/> Portuguese&#44; you would not<lb/> likely find it among Cathi<add>&#63;</add><lb/> <del>generally</del> gentry who are<lb/> proverbially exclusive.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I think it would<lb/> be better for you to address<lb/> the <persName>Benjamins</persName> direct&#8212;<lb/>  Address <persName>Benjamin Bros</persName>&#8212;<lb/> <placeName>Manchester</placeName>.  If you like<lb/> however&#44; as I correspond</p>
			<pb n="3"/>
				<p>with them I will address them<lb/> for you.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">How is it we get the <sic>occident</sic> here in the middle of the<lb/> month&#63;  I would like to get it<lb/> early so that if there are errors<lb/> in the Biography they may be<lb/> altered before going to press for<lb/> the pamphlet.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">For the present farewell</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">I remain yours truly</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><persName role="author">Abraham de Sola</persName></p>
		</body>
	</text>
